=Episode 38=

21
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:05,310
You finally woke up.

22
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:10,470
Do you know who I am?

23
00:02:20,880 --> 00:02:21,830
You are Meng Wanyue,

24
00:02:23,110 --> 00:02:24,520
Jun Beiyue's mother.

25
00:02:26,910 --> 00:02:28,720
Since you know me,

26
00:02:28,720 --> 00:02:29,910
I won't beat around the bush then.

27
00:02:31,320 --> 00:02:32,190
Do you know?

28
00:02:32,190 --> 00:02:33,160
I saved you.

29
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:39,360
Where is this?

30
00:02:41,320 --> 00:02:42,160
Yangshan Mountain.

31
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:44,200
Yangshan Mountain?

32
00:02:46,720 --> 00:02:47,750
Why did you bring me here?

33
00:02:49,910 --> 00:02:51,960
The Crown Prince of Dongling
is indeed arrogant.

34
00:02:52,750 --> 00:02:54,670
I saved your life after all.

35
00:02:54,670 --> 00:02:56,360
You didn't even say thank you.

36
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,160
You saved me?

37
00:03:02,030 --> 00:03:03,630
What did you bring me here for?

38
00:03:05,720 --> 00:03:06,960
I am a Barrier Master.

39
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:09,240
I know it by a glance

40
00:03:09,240 --> 00:03:13,160
that your vital energy is sealed
by the Barrier within your body.

41
00:03:13,160 --> 00:03:14,240
Only then could you survive.

42
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:16,470
But that's not important.

43
00:03:16,470 --> 00:03:19,080
You probably don't know it yourself

44
00:03:19,750 --> 00:03:22,320
that when your vital energy was sealed,

45
00:03:22,320 --> 00:03:24,910
the Five Elements Essence in your body
was awakened,

46
00:03:26,270 --> 00:03:28,110
which greatly enhanced your abilities.

47
00:03:28,910 --> 00:03:30,160
Didn't you notice?

48
00:03:30,160 --> 00:03:31,660
Five Elements Essence?

49
00:03:31,670 --> 00:03:32,510
That's right.

50
00:03:32,670 --> 00:03:34,800
It is a very special vital energy

51
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:36,910
which is transformed
from the five elements.

52
00:03:37,440 --> 00:03:39,910
It only resides in the body
of the destined one.

53
00:03:39,910 --> 00:03:41,490
It's a rare chance in a millennium.

54
00:03:41,500 --> 00:03:42,340
And you are

55
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:44,320
the destined one.

56
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:47,800
I didn't expect that when I followed
Han Ziqing and the others to Xiling,

57
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:49,470
I would yield such a harvest.

58
00:03:49,700 --> 00:03:51,160
I don't understand
what you're talking about.

59
00:03:54,390 --> 00:03:55,960
Is this why you saved me?

60
00:03:55,960 --> 00:03:56,800
Smart.

61
00:03:57,960 --> 00:04:00,520
You have such a rare body
with Five Elements Essence.

62
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:02,470
If it can't be properly utilized,

63
00:04:02,470 --> 00:04:04,470
wouldn't it be a waste?

64
00:04:06,470 --> 00:04:08,000
So you will kill me?

65
00:04:13,880 --> 00:04:16,720
Silly child, how could I kill you?

66
00:04:17,950 --> 00:04:18,830
To be honest with you,

67
00:04:19,640 --> 00:04:23,110
I was afflicted with a Curse Poison
by the Minister of Nanzhao.

68
00:04:23,110 --> 00:04:24,550
And this Curse Poison

69
00:04:24,550 --> 00:04:26,320
will cause me to lose all my skills

70
00:04:27,200 --> 00:04:29,230
if I don't take the antidote regularly.

71
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:31,390
But now it's fine.

72
00:04:31,390 --> 00:04:33,070
Your Five Elements Essence

73
00:04:33,070 --> 00:04:35,110
can help me neutralize the poison

74
00:04:35,110 --> 00:04:36,390
and break the shackles.

75
00:04:36,390 --> 00:04:37,230
In your dreams!

76
00:04:40,550 --> 00:04:41,390
Alright.

77
00:04:41,640 --> 00:04:43,040
Don't waste your energy.

78
00:04:43,040 --> 00:04:44,760
You have lost a lot of vital energy.

79
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:46,160
Without my help,

80
00:04:46,160 --> 00:04:47,600
you won't be able to leave this cave.

81
00:05:04,510 --> 00:05:07,230
Silly child, you can't hurt me.

82
00:05:08,070 --> 00:05:10,160
After all, I am a Barrier Master.

83
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:12,920
I can instantly set up a Barrier
on my body.

84
00:05:15,880 --> 00:05:18,440
I am determined
to take your Five Elements Essence.

85
00:05:18,440 --> 00:05:19,320
Do you know why?

86
00:05:20,390 --> 00:05:22,390
Once I have cleaned the Curse Poison
from my body,

87
00:05:22,390 --> 00:05:24,880
I have a monumental work to do.

88
00:05:25,510 --> 00:05:27,920
You are familiar with Han Ziqing,
aren't you?

89
00:05:27,920 --> 00:05:28,760
What are you going to do?

90
00:05:30,950 --> 00:05:32,350
You do have feelings for her.

91
00:05:33,110 --> 00:05:34,600
Then I must tell you even more.

92
00:05:35,320 --> 00:05:36,790
Once I have
neutralized the Curse Poison,

93
00:05:36,790 --> 00:05:37,920
the first thing I will do

94
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:39,760
is to use Han Ziqing to create a puppet.

95
00:05:40,390 --> 00:05:43,270
She is the only Islander
on the Longyuan Continent.

96
00:05:43,270 --> 00:05:45,440
She is also the other destined one.

97
00:05:46,850 --> 00:05:48,200
Stay away from her.

98
00:05:48,200 --> 00:05:49,320
Stay away from her!

99
00:05:50,390 --> 00:05:51,950
It's not up to you.

100
00:05:51,950 --> 00:05:52,790
Xuanyuan Lige,

101
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:54,760
